title.narrative: Management of Short term Training Awards

description.narrative: New Zealand Short Term Training Scholarships (NZSTTS) scholars are placed and provided with on-award management and support in order that they successfully complete training in New Zealand, gaining new skills that can be utilised in the development of their home countries. Off-shore or blended training may be developed to respond to border restrictions unanticipated when this Activity was created.
